title: 100. Now and Later - Sage the Gemini
text: by Pink star⭐️ I can't stop listening to this song! Super catchy and get to dance to! Keep the great work up Sage! Biography Born: June 20, 1992 in Fairfield, CA Genre: Hip-Hop/Rap Years Active: '10s Coming out of California's Bay Area, rapper Sage the Gemini broke through with two viral party singles, "Gas Pedal" and "Red Nose." "Gas Pedal" landed first, with the audio being uploaded to video-sharing sites in 2012; the track combined Sage's restrained delivery with an infectious, Ying Yang Twins or hyphy-type hook.
